      "rendered": "10 Must-Add Nonprofits on Snapchat"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/10-Must-Add-Nonprofits-on-Snapchat.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19791\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-19791\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/10-Must-Add-Nonprofits-on-Snapchat-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"10 Must-Add Nonprofits on Snapchat\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/10-Must-Add-Nonprofits-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/10-Must-Add-Nonprofits-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/10-Must-Add-Nonprofits-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/10-Must-Add-Nonprofits-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/10-Must-Add-Nonprofits-on-Snapchat.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>It&#8217;s not easy to tell a good Snapchat story,\u00a0</em>but the nonprofits listed below are making a concerted effort to pioneer Snapchat storytelling. Doing so requires a willingness to experiment beyond traditional social media marketing and an understanding that there is no immediate payoff in terms of fundraising. In time, <strong><a href=\"https://support.snapchat.com/en-US/about/snapcash\" target=\"_blank\">Snapcash</a></strong> may be used for fundraising, but for now\u00a0it&#8217;s all about being an early adopter.\u00a0Is your nonprofit considering experimenting with Snapchat? Here&#8217;s <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2016/04/11/how-to-get-your-nonprofit-started-on-snapchat/\">how to get started</a></strong>\u00a0\u2013 then add and study the\u00a0Snapchatters below and learn from their snaps.</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. United Nations\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/unitednations\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/unitednations</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/unitednations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19779\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19779\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/United-Nations-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"United Nations on Snapchat\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/United-Nations-on-Snapchat.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/United-Nations-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Service Works?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/serviceworks\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/serviceworks</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/serviceworks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19801\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19801\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Service-Works-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Service Works on Snapchat\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Service-Works-on-Snapchat.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Service-Works-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. PETA\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/officialpeta\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/officialpeta</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/officialpeta\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19760\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19760\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Peta.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Peta\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Peta.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Peta.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Ocean Conservancy\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/oceanconservancy\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/oceanconservancy</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/oceanconservancy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19762\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19762\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Ocean-Conservancy.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Ocean Conservancy\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Ocean-Conservancy.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Ocean-Conservancy.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Oceana\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/oceana\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/oceana</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/oceana\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19784\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19784\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Oceana-on-Snapchat-PNG.png?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Oceana on Snapchat PNG\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Oceana-on-Snapchat-PNG.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Oceana-on-Snapchat-PNG.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Los Angeles County Museum of Art\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/LACMA\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/LACMA</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/LACMA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19767\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19767\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/LACMA.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"LACMA\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/LACMA.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/LACMA.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Human Rights Campaign\u00a0\u200d?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/humanrightscampaign\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/humanrightscampaign</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/humanrightscampaign\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19765\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19765\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/HRC-Snapchat-2.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"HRC Snapchat 2\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/HRC-Snapchat-2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/HRC-Snapchat-2.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Greenpeace\u00a0\u267b\ufe0f<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/greenpeace\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/greenpeace</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/greenpeace\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19775\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19775\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/GREENPEACE-PNG.png?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"GREENPEACE PNG\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/GREENPEACE-PNG.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/GREENPEACE-PNG.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. FOUR PAWS\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/fourpaws\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/fourpaws</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/fourpaws\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19776\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19776\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Four-Paws-Snapchat.png?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Four Paws Snapchat\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Four-Paws-Snapchat.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Four-Paws-Snapchat.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Charity Water?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/charitywater\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/charitywater</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/charitywater\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19754\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19754\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Charity-Water.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Charity Water\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Charity-Water.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Charity-Water.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #339966;\"><span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">?\u00a0</span></span><span style=\"color: #339966;\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900;\">Bonus!\u00a0</span></span><span style=\"color: #339966;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">5 Must-Add Government and Publisher\u00a0Snapchat <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Accounts\u00a0</span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #339966;\"><span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">?</span></span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. The Dodo\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/thedodo\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/thedodo</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/thedodo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19756\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19756\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Dodo.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Dodo\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Dodo.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Dodo.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. The Interior Department\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/usinterior\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/usinterior</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/usinterior\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19802\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19802\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Interior-Department-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Interior Department on Snapchat\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Interior-Department-on-Snapchat.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Interior-Department-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Mashable\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.snapchat.com/en-US/a/discover-how-to\" target=\"_blank\">Stories &gt; Discover</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://support.snapchat.com/en-US/a/discover-how-to\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19771\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19771\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Mashable.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Mashable\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Mashable.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Mashable.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. National Geographic\u00a0?<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.snapchat.com/en-US/a/discover-how-to\" target=\"_blank\">Stories &gt; Discover</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://support.snapchat.com/en-US/a/discover-how-to\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19770\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19770\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/National-Geographic-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"National Geographic on Snapchat\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/National-Geographic-on-Snapchat.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/National-Geographic-on-Snapchat.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. The White House\u00a0??<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/whitehouse\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/whitehouse</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/whitehouse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19768\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19768\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/White-House-Snapchat.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"White House Snapchat\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/White-House-Snapchat.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/White-House-Snapchat.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">And Finally&#8230; Nonprofit Tech for Good!?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\">snapchat.com/add/nonprofitorgs</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.snapchat.com/add/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19786\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19786\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Nonprofit-Tech-for-Good.jpg?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Nonprofit Tech for Good\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Nonprofit-Tech-for-Good.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Nonprofit-Tech-for-Good.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /> </a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>It&#8217;s not easy to tell a good Snapchat story,\u00a0but the nonprofits listed below are making a concerted effort to pioneer Snapchat storytelling. Doing so requires a willingness to experiment beyond traditional social media marketing and an understanding that there is no immediate payoff in terms of fundraising. In time, Snapcash may be used for fundraising, but for now\u00a0it&#8217;s all about being an early adopter.\u00a0Is your nonprofit considering experimenting with Snapchat? Here&#8217;s how to get started\u00a0\u2013 then add and study the\u00a0Snapchatters below and learn from their snaps. 1. United Nations\u00a0? snapchat.com/add/unitednations 2. Service Works? snapchat.com/add/serviceworks 3. PETA\u00a0? snapchat.com/add/officialpeta 4. Ocean Conservancy\u00a0? </p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
